# Ensure we don't copy local db into docker build if we're not meant to, but actually we WANT the db to be used, but since it's mounted, we can ignore the local db during build to avoid large image size if there's a huge db file.
# We'll rely on Prisma schema for build, and mount db at runtime.
db/*.db
prisma/*.db
